- What is this?

54
00:03:05.852 --> 00:03:10.389
Something seems odd.

55
00:03:11.608 --> 00:03:13.669
Are you sure you came for ricecake?

56
00:03:13.693 --> 00:03:16.589
Yes, of course.

57
00:03:16.613 --> 00:03:19.133
- Let's make it three.
- Okay.

58
