544
00:29:10.707 --> 00:29:11.809
As if.

545
00:29:11.833 --> 00:29:14.103
You did this too, didn't you?

546
00:29:14.127 --> 00:29:15.438
Yes, I did it. So what?

547
00:29:15.462 --> 00:29:19.692
I presented the idea to the
villagers to close down this place.

548
00:29:19.716 --> 00:29:23.779
