the consequences. Got it?

573
00:30:21.736 --> 00:30:24.021
Darn it!

574
00:30:24.113 --> 00:30:26.801
Ms. Jin!

575
00:30:26.825 --> 00:30:28.442
Ms. Jin!

576
00:30:28.577 --> 00:30:29.553
Ms. Jin!

577
00:30:29.577 --> 00:30:31.013
This is bad.

578
